{"tid":560253,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"吊 wechat pay又派利是","createTime":"2018-02-14T02:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T14:58:47.000Z","uid":38740,"like":6,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"116235b659d595e410caf86a12f35b8ccbe36c05","tid":560253,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"老實講香港市民唔值得擁有wechatpay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人識感恩"},{"pid":"eaf6a9514e4316905cdefbb91203a9e2affaa980","tid":560253,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"今次又派咩"},{"pid":"412c80ce4b0f591fe2c306136cc24a1d39bc0b2a","tid":560253,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf6a9514e4316905cdefbb91203a9e2affaa980","tid":560253,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"今次又派咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"Column<br />\n Ray手記: Ray<br />\n<br />\n電子利是 八達通WeChat都派得<br />\n4 小時前<br />\n#Hashtags<br />\n電子利是農曆新年利是紅包八達通WeChatMastercardVisaWeChatPaye利是搶利是<br />\n           news-images<br />\n農曆新年快到，已婚人士準備派利是，Ray今年就想試下收電子利是，除了大家都聽過同試過嘅WeChat Pay HK「紅包」之外，今年仲可以試埋土炮嘅八達通O! ePay「e利是」功能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先介紹下八達通個新功能，由即日起至下月23日期間就可以用，用戶只要喺App設定，可以輕鬆逐個派，或「刺激成疊派」(自定不同金額和數量俾親友即時掃描QR Code隨機抽)，每次最多可派500封「e利是」㗎。此外，App內仲設有24款心意滿瀉的新年貼紙，俾大家派利是同時送上祝福㖭。仲有喎，用嚟行善都得，就係將e利是捐俾WWF。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於WeChat Pay HK的「紅包」功能亦差不多，逐封派或大家齊齊玩「搶利是」都得，仲唔單止，WeChat Pay HK自己都大派利是，用戶只要用WeChat App掃描WeChat Pay HK或合作商戶發布的推廣活動QR code，即有機會獲得8.8港元(下同)WeChat Pay利是，或到指定商戶以WeChat Pay購物滿68元，就有機會獲贈28元利是，又或者用Mastercard或Visa首次綁定WeChat Pay HK錢包，亦有機會獲贈10元。"},{"pid":"8d62a6933295ccf15ff617e8b5f573811f79b30f","tid":560253,"uid":41428,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:55:05.000Z","msg":"鍾意咪用 唔鍾意咪唔用 感乜撚嘢恩？"},{"pid":"32b5f9b1e6eb661a576b64b46c9b05a6fa2c9066","tid":560253,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"老老實實,香港10幾隻epayment method, wechat pay hk都算係最垃圾果個"},{"pid":"9d76680229cfead6e7ed45b641d692f3a4ce8500","tid":560253,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以影個qr code上來刷8.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58002efacf71daded163c440b6e65061d4471534","tid":560253,"uid":156376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32b5f9b1e6eb661a576b64b46c9b05a6fa2c9066","tid":560253,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"老老實實,香港10幾隻epayment method, wechat pay hk都算係最垃圾果個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺"},{"pid":"f89eb3dd5640cad523e60f0559db06d8be5ad557","tid":560253,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fe4063c93d1d18f0aa9610bca74e0d898f0c9b","tid":560253,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d76680229cfead6e7ed45b641d692f3a4ce8500","tid":560253,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以影個qr code上來刷8.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:59:24.000Z","msg":"我想要商場果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a20c389278c5e5ef1f681991a3722f0220c1e6","tid":560253,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28fe4063c93d1d18f0aa9610bca74e0d898f0c9b","tid":560253,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d76680229cfead6e7ed45b641d692f3a4ce8500","tid":560253,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以影個qr code上來刷8.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:59:24.000Z",